#. module: theme_beauty
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_beauty.s_pricelist_boxed
msgid ""
"A lightweight, long-lasting foundation that provides full coverage while "
"allowing your skin to breathe."
msgstr ""
"Een lichtgewicht, langhoudende foundation die een volledige dekking biedt en "
"je huid toch laat ademen."

#. module: theme_beauty
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_beauty.s_pricelist_boxed
msgid ""
"A rejuvenating facial treatment designed to reduce wrinkles and fine lines, "
"leaving your skin looking fresh and youthful."
msgstr ""
"Een verjongende gezichtsbehandeling om rimpels en fijne lijntjes te "
"verminderen, zodat je huid er fris en jeugdig uitziet."

#. module: theme_beauty
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_beauty.s_pricelist_boxed
msgid ""
"A revitalizing facial that uses vitamin C and natural extracts to enhance "
"radiance and even out skin tone."
msgstr ""
"Een revitaliserende gezichtsbehandeling die vitamine C en natuurlijke "
"extracten gebruikt om de huid te laten stralen en de teint te egaliseren."

#. module: theme_beauty
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_beauty.s_pricelist_boxed
msgid "Anti-Aging Facial"
msgstr "Anti-verouderings gezichtsbehandeling"

#. module: theme_beauty
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_beauty.s_call_to_action
msgid "Beauty without <br/>expression is boring"
msgstr "Schoonheid zonder <br/>expressie is saai"

#. module: theme_beauty
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_beauty.s_pricelist_boxed
msgid "Brightening Facial"
msgstr "Verhelderende gezichtsbehandeling"

#. module: theme_beauty
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_beauty.s_intro_pill
msgid "Confidence and<br/>Timeless Elegance"
msgstr "Vertrouwen en<br/>Tijdloze elegantie"

#. module: theme_beauty
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_beauty.s_pricelist_boxed
msgid ""
"Deeply hydrating facial treatment that restores moisture and balances your "
"skin, perfect for dry or sensitive skin types."
msgstr ""
"Diep hydraterende gezichtsbehandeling die het vochtgehalte herstelt en je "
"huid in balans brengt, perfect voor droge of gevoelige huidtypes."

#. module: theme_beauty
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_beauty.s_intro_pill
msgid "Discover our products"
msgstr "Ontdek onze producten"

#. module: theme_beauty
#: model:ir.model.fields,field_description:theme_beauty.field_theme_utils__display_name
msgid "Display Name"
msgstr "Schermnaam"

#. module: theme_beauty
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_beauty.s_pricelist_boxed
msgid ""
"Enhance your natural beauty with our range of luxurious cosmetic services "
"and products. Expertly crafted for every skin type and style."
msgstr ""
"Verbeter je natuurlijke schoonheid met ons assortiment luxe cosmetische "
"diensten en producten. Deskundig samengesteld voor elk huidtype en elke "
"stijl."

#. module: theme_beauty
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_beauty.s_features_wall
msgid ""
"Explore our luxurious makeup selection, offering vibrant colors and long-"
"lasting formulas for a flawless look every day."
msgstr ""
"Ontdek onze luxe make-up selectie, met levendige kleuren en langhoudende "
"formules voor een vlekkeloze look elke dag."

#. module: theme_beauty
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_beauty.s_features_wall
msgid ""
"Find your signature scent with our exclusive range of perfumes, crafted to "
"leave a lasting impression all day long."
msgstr ""
"Vind je eigen geur met ons exclusieve assortiment parfums, gemaakt om de "
"hele dag een blijvende indruk achter te laten."

#. module: theme_beauty
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_beauty.s_features_wall
msgid "Fragrances and Scents"
msgstr "Geuren en Geuren"

#. module: theme_beauty
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_beauty.s_pricelist_boxed
msgid ""
"High-quality mascara that adds volume and length to your lashes, with a "
"smudge-proof and long-lasting formula."
msgstr ""
"Hoogwaardige mascara die je wimpers volume en lengte geeft, met een "
"veegvaste en langhoudende formule."

#. module: theme_beauty
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_beauty.s_pricelist_boxed
msgid "Hydrating Facial"
msgstr "Hydraterende gezichtsbehandeling"

#. module: theme_beauty
#: model:ir.model.fields,field_description:theme_beauty.field_theme_utils__id
msgid "ID"
msgstr "ID"

#. module: theme_beauty
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_beauty.s_call_to_action
msgid "Join us and enjoy the pleasure of caring for yourself."
msgstr "Kom en geniet van het plezier om voor jezelf te zorgen."

#. module: theme_beauty
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_beauty.s_pricelist_boxed
msgid "Long-Lasting Foundation"
msgstr "Duurzame fundering"

#. module: theme_beauty
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_beauty.s_features_wall
msgid "Natural Skincare Products"
msgstr "Natuurlijke huidverzorgingsproducten"

#. module: theme_beauty
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_beauty.s_pricelist_boxed
msgid "Our Beauty Collection"
msgstr "Onze schoonheidscollectie"

#. module: theme_beauty
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_beauty.s_features_wall
msgid "Premium Makeup Collection"
msgstr "Premium make-up collectie"

#. module: theme_beauty
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_beauty.s_features_wall
msgid ""
"Revitalize your skin with our range of organic, chemical-free skincare "
"products designed for all skin types."
msgstr ""
"Revitaliseer je huid met ons assortiment biologische, chemicaliënvrije "
"huidverzorgingsproducten voor alle huidtypes."

#. module: theme_beauty
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_beauty.s_pricelist_boxed
msgid ""
"Richly pigmented matte lipstick available in various shades, providing a "
"bold, long-lasting finish without drying out your lips."
msgstr ""
"Rijk gepigmenteerde matte lippenstift verkrijgbaar in verschillende tinten, "
"voor een opvallende, langhoudende finish zonder je lippen uit te drogen."

#. module: theme_beauty
#: model:ir.model,name:theme_beauty.model_theme_utils
msgid "Theme Utils"
msgstr "Thematools"

#. module: theme_beauty
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_beauty.s_pricelist_boxed
msgid "Velvet Matte Lipstick"
msgstr "Fluweelmatte lippenstift"

#. module: theme_beauty
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_beauty.s_pricelist_boxed
msgid "Volumizing Mascara"
msgstr "Volumizing Mascara"

#. module: theme_beauty
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_beauty.s_pricelist_boxed
msgid "✽  Facial Treatments"
msgstr "gezichtsbehandelingen"

#. module: theme_beauty
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_beauty.s_pricelist_boxed
msgid "✽  Makeup Products"
msgstr "make-up producten"
